WEBVTT

00:00.635 --> 00:02.234
Previously, on Genius...

00:03.237 --> 00:04.569
You are a genius, Maya.

00:04.606 --> 00:05.638
Come here.

00:05.773 --> 00:07.456
You have children,
women you love.

00:07.591 --> 00:09.658
Some things are more
important than art.

00:09.661 --> 00:11.627
Not to me.

00:11.763 --> 00:12.962
Pablo?

00:12.964 --> 00:14.964
You must be Marie-Thérèse.

00:14.966 --> 00:16.799
The mother of his child, the
woman he is going to marry.

00:16.801 --> 00:19.602
Perhaps you should pay a visit
to his wife and inform her of

00:19.604 --> 00:21.737
this... expectation.

00:21.973 --> 00:24.457
Pablo Picasso,
meet Henri Matisse.

00:24.792 --> 00:28.760
40 years on, and the great Henri
Matisse is still trying to outdo me.

00:30.798 --> 00:33.999
As artists, we must demand
nothing less than the perpetual,

00:34.068 --> 00:36.936
immoral subversion of
the existing order.

00:37.939 --> 00:39.771
I hope she makes you happy.

00:39.807 --> 00:43.459
You will get married, and you will
have a family but not with me.

00:43.845 --> 00:45.361
I'm about to
leave for The Front.

00:45.363 --> 00:47.029
I was hoping you would
paint my portrait?

00:47.164 --> 00:48.730
The woman I love is dying.

00:48.766 --> 00:50.646
You think I want to paint
your goddamn portrait?

00:50.768 --> 00:52.868
Maybe I should be a soldier.

00:52.904 --> 00:55.805
Well, then you will be general, and
if you're a priest, you will be pope.

00:56.474 --> 00:57.857
I had a vision.

00:57.859 --> 00:59.191
Jesus appeared to me.

00:59.193 --> 01:00.793
I want you to
stay away from Picasso.

01:00.862 --> 01:02.127
Stop!

01:02.196 --> 01:03.863
I have missed you, terribly.

01:03.865 --> 01:05.731
I only want you, Françoise.

01:05.800 --> 01:07.333
Let's make a baby.

01:07.335 --> 01:08.945
You were the one
who wanted children, Pablo,

01:08.969 --> 01:10.569
but I didn't agree
to give up my work,

01:10.605 --> 01:12.838
so I could
cater to all your needs.

